# Brian Lister's TOP Project Portfolio

## [Live View ➠](https://fabulousgk.github.io/top-projects)

Welcome to my coding journey showcased in this repository—a compilation of projects that map my progress through [The Odin Project](https://www.theodinproject.com/), a comprehensive full-stack web developer curriculum. This space isn't merely a code vault; it's a dynamic chronicle of my growth and the obstacles I encountered along the way. Think of each project as a chapter, a snapshot immortalizing the evolution of my skills.

Following a temporary hiatus prompted by illness, I took a bold step to restart the curriculum, and this repository chronicles that fresh start. Throughout this journey, I've set a challenge for myself—to exclusively use the tools and techniques available at each stage of the curriculum. This dual purpose serves as a personal challenge and a commitment to delivering high-quality examples for fellow learners.

As a contributor to The Odin Project, I've eagerly embraced the chance to assist new learners on their coding adventures. Consequently, this repository stands as a testament to my personal growth and my dedication to supporting others on the rewarding path of web development.
